{"tid":1325550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"腦友坊想紅，大家幫幫手","createTime":"2019-07-17T02:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T02:12:35.000Z","uid":275292,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0a9da2ee34478a3bdecc389d57e1e5d81d297cb8","tid":1325550,"uid":275292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:12:35.000Z","msg":"* 榮譽顧問 除名通告 *<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">過去幾個月發生一連串反對『逃犯條例』示威活動，消息令人不安</span>，而本會顧問張超雄先生亦有參與其中，亦發表了他對今次事件的看法和作出相應的行動，本會上下委員對他於今次事件的一連串行為和言論，本會深表遺憾。因此，本會宣佈由即日開始，褫奪腦友坊榮譽顧問張超雄先生資格，即日生効！以後張超雄先生一切言論和行動都與腦友坊慈善有限公司無關，謹此通知！<br />\n<br />\n腦友坊慈善有限公司全體執行委員會敬上<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.loyaufong.org.hk/aboutus/committee.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.loyaufong.org.hk%2Faboutus%2Fcommittee.html&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=a11c7a5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.loyaufong.org.hk/aboutus/committee.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2768538829845218&amp;id=971897269509392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2768538829845218%26id%3D971897269509392&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=693b472e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2768538829845218&amp;id=971897269509392</a>"}]}